{"tid":686931,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"除淨前除淨後買煤氣分別","createTime":"2018-06-01T17:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T21:15:14.000Z","uid":10366,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f61f18fb75f4b03e24dc91a568cbe9b76555129e","tid":686931,"uid":10366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"睇完之前煤氣升咁急個post同買煤氣意見個post 都有巴打講其實除淨前後買分別不大 諗緊係咪真<br />\n<br />\n最近恆生開戶做緊免佣 心郁郁都想買返啲藍籌 煤氣都係心水之一 因為見好多人吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我整左個excel 去睇吓除淨前後買煤氣到底有咩分別 <br />\n<br />\n我當買完渣5年 咁4叔都老 有巴打話佢一日在生一日都會keep十送一 當佢黎緊呢5年 直到2023年都健健康康 再假設5年入面(2019-2023) 只有3年(2019,2021,2023)有十送一 <br />\n<br />\n我假設未來呢幾年煤氣會0增長keep住15蚊 然後我2018除淨前17蚊買十手 (啲手續費我用恆生套收費計 同埋我冇將利息納入計算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/012910_38fdc78fe190681be75d3a930c11e662.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F012910_38fdc78fe190681be75d3a930c11e662.png&h=28223db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018變左11000股係因為今年10送一<br />\n最尾到2023年年尾 回報率係28.42%<br />\n<br />\n如果我當除淨前個價同今日收市一樣係17.02 咁除淨後就應該得返(17.02-0.23)x10/11=15.26 我當我除淨後15.26買十手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/014439_fe79a0e0690780858434e065db2a304e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F014439_fe79a0e0690780858434e065db2a304e.png&h=585e8c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾到2023年年尾 回報率係30.04%<br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣係咪意味住除淨前or後買其實真係分別不大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1125d0ad72722600f4713db9d842eccc23e64285","tid":686931,"uid":5278,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:48:59.000Z","msg":"其實呢個計法已經係假設左3號年年有10%增長<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"